{"tid":1692657,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"大家一定要支持玻璃回收！！！","createTime":"2019-11-04T07:37:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T08:17:54.000Z","uid":305417,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"53f895a6fb9bbcd37bf09452622f9049f52148af","tid":1692657,"uid":305417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:37:55.000Z","msg":"根據環保署於「香港固體廢物監察報告2017」公布的數字，香港棄於堆填區的玻璃樽總重高達80,300公噸，即每日有220公噸。<br />\n<br />\n如果以一個330ml啤酒樽計算，每日約有666,667個玻璃樽長埋堆填區。玻璃是一種惰性物料，它不會自然分解，隨意丟棄玻璃樽會耗用日益減少的堆填區空間，亦會浪費珍貴的資源。為達到減廢目標，環保署已正式委聘「碧瑤廢物處理及回收有限公司」(碧瑤)為香港區(包括離島)及新界區指定的玻璃管理承辦商，積極推動及鼓勵玻璃樽乾淨回收，負責為市民及工商機構提供玻璃樽回收及處理服務。<br />\n<br />\n以下係回收地點地圖：<br />\n<a href=\"http://gmc.baguio.com.hk/%e7%8e%bb%e7%92%83%e6%a8%bd%e5%9b%9e%e6%94%b6%e9%bb%9e-%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e5%8d%80%e5%9c%b0%e5%9c%96/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgmc.baguio.com.hk%2F%25e7%258e%25bb%25e7%2592%2583%25e6%25a8%25bd%25e5%259b%259e%25e6%2594%25b6%25e9%25bb%259e-%25e9%25a6%2599%25e6%25b8%25af%25e5%258d%2580%25e5%259c%25b0%25e5%259c%2596%2F&d=yqGHcbR114BEm%2FDIyWJWfjRqNRg6ChYs1Sy50pDDGUM%3D&h=d614ff73\" target=\"_blank\">http://gmc.baguio.com.hk/%e7%8e%bb%e7%92%83%e6%a8%bd%e5%9b%9e%e6%94%b6%e9%bb%9e-%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e5%8d%80%e5%9c%b0%e5%9c%96/</a><br />\n<br />\n一定要回收哂，唔可以俾人攞黎做武器<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e04537a9dee26ca9c26448692e2f5f474a27873","tid":1692657,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:45:38.000Z","msg":"咁多玻璃樽 <br />\n有咩用呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c7a55e8a2a5b87dd1a939ffe2fa652aece0e5e6","tid":1692657,"uid":305417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e04537a9dee26ca9c26448692e2f5f474a27873","tid":1692657,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:45:38.000Z","msg":"咁多玻璃樽 <br />\n有咩用呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" 